      <div class="text-center mb-8 sm:mb-10 lg:mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 sm:mb-4">Every Type of Therapy, All in One Place</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground max-w-4xl mx-auto text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg px-4">From conventional therapies to personal development, find your therapy</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-8 sm:mb-10 lg:mb-12">
