        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed px-4">The easiest way to find, book, and connect with verified wellness professionals. Like Booking.com meets Meetup.com, but designed specifically for therapy and healing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-8 sm:mb-12 px-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 sm:flex-nowrap sm:gap-2 bg-white rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl p-1.5 sm:p-2 shadow-lg w-full sm:w-auto overflow-x-auto">
